window.bookSummaryJSON = "Welcome to Avatar: The Podcast! Join hosts AcornBandit and BoosterGreg as they explore the world of Avatar: The Last Airbender and thoughtfully revisit the characters, themes, and events that make Avatar such an impactful show. Whether you’re re-watching the series or you’re brand new to the adventures of Team Avatar, this is one journey through the Avatar universe you won’t want to miss! Part of The Geek Generation Network."; 
